@startuml
title Save slides to PDF

hide footbox

participant VideoPdfConverter
participant SlideSelector
participant PdfCreator
participant "PDF file" as PdfFile

VideoPdfConverter -> SlideSelector: find_slides(video_path)
SlideSelector --> VideoPdfConverter: slides

alt slides found
    VideoPdfConverter -> PdfCreator: save(slides, output_path)
    PdfCreator -> PdfFile: create result.pdf
    PdfFile --> PdfCreator: saved
    PdfCreator --> VideoPdfConverter: true
else no slides
    PdfCreator --> VideoPdfConverter: false
end

@enduml
